metadata.name: #01 Pepe Bathtime
metadata.description:
नर्मदे सिन्धु कावेरि जलऽस्मिन्सन्निधिं कुरु।
It is said that this mantra should be chanted while PEPE is taking a bath and the meaning of this mantra is, "O Ganges, Yamuna, Godavari, Saraswati, Narmada, Indus, Kaveri rivers! PEPE" 
All of you enter this water of my bath.

*By 3va Polyanskaya and DenManu
